accessibility.text: Main Goal: Attend his meeting at 9 am, 1st November 2018
Gonalo is a very hard worker so he wakes up at 7 am and gets ready to leave his house for a possibly career changing meeting
He arrives at his closest metro station, Alvalade, and he tries to validate his ticket and go through the gate
He soon realizes his monthly pass expired with the start of the new month
He moves to the ticket machines so he can pay his monthly fee but there is a huge line and he is starting to be late for the meeting
Finally, he pays and validates his pass and enters the metro
When he finally reaches the meeting, he was already 20 minutes late for it, decreasing his reputation as the hard-worker
